02:14:19,000 --> 02:14:22,583
♪ You are a star
That twinkles in the skies ♪

1795
02:14:24,333 --> 02:14:28,333
♪ Through the curves
Of my tender heart ♪

1796
02:14:28,500 --> 02:14:31,916
♪ You rise and crash
Like oceans start ♪

1797
